				<a class='comment-reply-link' href='/2013/01/06/19981-comme-pour-la-presse-la-subvention-a-massacre-le-cinema-francais?replytocom=98551#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("comment-98551", "98551", "respond", "19981")'>Répondre</a>							</div>
